#########General 
ranger general~Q,<F10>~quit!
ranger general~q~quit
ranger general~Rd, <F5>~reload current working directorie
ranger general~<C-r>~reset
ranger general~Rw~redraw window ( Usefuul  when previwws disapier )
ranger general~<C-c>~abort, cancel
ranger general~<esc>~change mode to normal
#########View,Help,Log,Taskview
ranger general~vf,<F3>~display file in full screen 
ranger general~?, <F1>~activate help menu 
ranger general~W~display log in full screen
ranger general~tv~taskview open, view current task
ranger general~S~enter shell execution mode
#########Console Basics
ranger general~:~enter console
ranger general~;~enter console
ranger general~!~enter console  shell with a space 
ranger general~@~enter shell with current file after cursor
ranger general~<INSERT>~console touch Create a file!
#########On the fly Settings 
ranger general~zc~toggle collapse preview
ranger general~zd~toggle sort directories first
ranger general~zh, <C-h>~toggle show hidden
ranger general~zi~toggle flushinput
ranger general~zm~toggle	mouse_enabled
ranger general~zp~toggle	preview_files
ranger general~zP~toggle	preview_directories
ranger general~zs~toggle	sort_case_insensitive
ranger general~zu~toggle	autoupdate_cumulative_size
ranger general~zv~toggle	use_preview_script
ranger general~zf~console filter and space
#########Tagging  ( t )
ranger tag~tt~toggle Tags ( Creates a mark )
ranger tag~tr~remove tag
ranger tag~t"<any>~use a custom mark tag
#########line mode( M )
ranger mode~Mlf~filename
ranger mode~Mli~fileinfo
ranger mode~Mlp~permissions
ranger mode~Mlt~metatitle
ranger mode~Mld~devicons DEFAULT
#########Sorting ( s )
ranger sort~sr~reverse false
ranger sort~sz~random false
ranger sort~ss~size false
ranger sort~sb~basename	false
ranger sort~sn~natural false
ranger sort~sm~mtime false
ranger sort~sc~ctime false
ranger sort~sa~atime false
ranger sort~st~type false
ranger sort~se~extension false
ranger sort~sS~size	True
ranger sort~sB~basename	True
ranger sort~sN~natural True
ranger sort~sM~mtime	True
ranger sort~sC~ctime	True
ranger sort~sA~atime	True
ranger sort~sT~type	True
ranger sort~sE~extension	True
ranger sort~Z~Special cumulative size
#########Bookmarks ( m )
ranger bookmark~me<any>~enter bookmark %any
ranger bookmark~mn<any>~set 	bookmark %any
ranger bookmark~mu<any>~unset bookmark %any
ranger bookmark~md~draw	bookmarks
#########Searching
ranger seacrh~/~console search%space
ranger search~f~console find%
#########FZF Integration
ranger search~<C-l>~fzf selection
ranger search~<C-g>~fzf location
#########Movement
ranger movement~<UP>,k~move up a space
ranger movement~<DOWN>,j~move down a space
ranger movement~<LEFT>,h~move lef a page
ranger movement~<RIGHT>,l~move right a page
ranger movement~<HOME>,gg~move to first line
ranger movement~<END>,G~move to the bottom line
ranger movement~<PAGEDOWN>,<C-f>~move down a page
ranger movement~<PAGEUP>,<C-b>~move up a page
ranger movement~<CR>~move right a space
ranger movement~J,<C-d>~move down half screen
ranger movement~K,<C-u>~move up half screen
ranger movement~cdr~enters Ranger User root directorie
#########Tabs
ranger movement~<C-n>,gn~Create new tab
ranger movement~<C-w>,Tc~Close current tab
ranger movement~Tr~restore a Tab
ranger movement~<TAB>,<A-Right>,Tn~move fordward a tab 
ranger movement~<S-TAB>,<A-Left>,Tb~move backward a tab
ranger movement~<a-number>~!
#########Filesystem Operations
ranger ops~an~console rename plus space
ranger ops~aa~rename append
ranger ops~aW~bulkrename
ranger ops~pp~paste
ranger ops~po~paste overwrite true 
ranger ops~pP~paste append True
ranger ops~pO~paste overwrite True append True
ranger ops~pl~paste_symlink relative False
ranger ops~pL~paste_symlink relative=True
ranger ops~phl~paste_hardlink
ranger ops~pht~paste_hardlinked_subtree
ranger ops~pd~console paste dest=
ranger ops~dc,<F6>~cut
ranger ops~du~uncut
ranger ops~da~cut add
ranger ops~dr~cut remove
ranger ops~dD, <F8>~console delete
ranger ops~<DELETE>~console delete
ranger ops~dd~send to trash
ranger ops~dR~restore from trash 
ranger ops~dE~empty trash
ranger ops~dL~trash list
ranger ops~yy,<F5>~copy
ranger ops~ya~copy add
ranger ops~yr~copy remove
ranger ops~ysf~show a list of copy files in cache
ranger ops~yp~Copy full file Path to system clipboard
ranger ops~yd~Copy full Directory Path to system clipboard
ranger ops~<Space>~mark a files 						
ranger ops~va~mark all files  
ranger ops~vA~unmark all files  
ranger ops~vs~toggle visual_mode 
ranger ops~vS~toggle visual_mode reverse True
ranger ops~E,<F4>~edit
ranger ops~V~Insert vim at console
ranger ops~owv~Open with vim Main server					
ranger ops~owo~Open With & choose
ranger ops~X~extract
ranger ops~Z~compresss
ranger ops~mkd,<F7>~Create a directorie
ranger ops~<INSERT>a~Create a file
ranger ops~cm+~chmod +x  Add execution permission
ranger ops~cm-~chmod -x  Remove execution permission
#########Tools
ranger tools~ep~cmus play
ranger tools~el~cmus lib
ranger tools~eq~cmus queue 
ranger tools~bg~feh background
ranger tools~br~rotate 90 Image
